parameters: This is some Indiana Jones-level stuff.
There’s treasure in here, I just know it.

And here comes the bad part.
Heh, guess it can’t reach us in here.

You’re not alone in this. We chose it together.
We’re still breathing. I’m not going anywhere.
That’s for being too stubborn to leave me behind.
Didn’t hate it though, did you?
She said my energy could help others recover...)

Unless you’ve got a potion tucked into your loincloth,

telling me you want to jerk one out for medicinal purposes?

Look—I wouldn’t bring it up if I wasn’t desperate, okay?
I hate that I’m considering this...
But after dragging you into this mess, I owe you.
I can’t believe you’re making me do this.
You asked for a way out—I’m giving you one.
Ugh. Fine. But I’m doing this quickly.
I swear, if this doesn’t work...
You’ll feel better. Just trust me.
Start with a lick. The tip is sensitive.
You can go a little faster.

An intimate technique that restores HP and MP.
Looks like the monsters are gone.
Heh, guess it can’t reach us in here.
This spot’s barely wide enough to breathe...
Better than being torn apart out there.
I'm just trying not to shake in front of you.
Every time... when you cum inside me...
I feel my strength come back.
My body drinks it in. Like it's meant for me.
It’s real. And we’re stuck here anyway...
So let me feel that warmth again.
Oh gods... is it always this big?
Just looking at it makes my throat tight...
You know you want to feel it.
Show me what that pretty mouth can do.
It’s so thick in my mouth...
You’re so good at this now...
I love the way you twitch on my tongue...
You’re so hard... filling my mouth so deep...
You’re gonna make me lose it if you keep that up...
I want all of it... right here.
Mmm... stho warm... nghh... sho thick...
gotta get my stamina back before anything else.
We have to get out of here!
